Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,四張同牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就告訴你吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,賭博可是需要冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大贏特贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:55.20,OP_Sim,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(200,400)}GOLDEN LIFE  未來在哪裡
